    dc:description "Figures 63–69. Stegana (Steganina) xanthosticta sp. nov., Ƌ. (63) Epandrium, surstylus and cercus; (64) surstylus; (65) tenth sternite; (66, 67) hypandrium, aedeagus and aedeagal apodeme; (68, 69) gonopods. For orientation and organization see Figures 8–14. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
